original_title: Bronx: City Island Avenue - Pell Street
text:
139 City Island Ave., at the S.W. corner of Pell Street, showing Bracker's Restaurant.

July 26, 1928.

P. L. Sperr.

original_title: Bronx: City Island Avenue - Pell Street
text:
City Island Avenue (City Island), west side, north from Pell to Winters Streets. The houses in the center background face on the north side of Winters Street; those on the extreme left, on the north side of Earley Street.

July 26, 1928

P. L. Sperr
